1
00:00:06,537 --> 00:00:07,601
Somewhere...

2
00:00:07,631 --> 00:00:09,733
The pilot said we're over
a thousand miles off course.

3
00:00:09,763 --> 00:00:12,963
- on a mysterious island...
- This place is different.

4
00:00:14,285 --> 00:00:17,345
- 48 passengers...
- If we can't live together...

5
00:00:17,465 --> 00:00:20,202
survived the crash
of Oceanic 815.

6
00:00:20,232 --> 00:00:21,832
... we're gonna die alone.

7
00:00:23,059 --> 00:00:27,008
- 108 days pass...
- I'm one of the survivors of flight 815.

8
00:00:27,128 --> 00:00:30,828
- and six people find rescue.
- So we can go off the island?

9
00:00:32,106 --> 00:00:34,006
- But their friends...
- Sawyer!

10
00:00:35,558 --> 00:00:36,956
are left behind.

11
00:00:37,075 --> 00:00:38,660
We need to go back!

12
00:00:39,963 --> 00:00:41,379
And the island...

13
00:00:41,418 --> 00:00:42,976
is suddenly...

14
00:00:44,206 --> 00:00:45,280
gone.

15
00:00:45,310 --> 00:00:47,620
- Wait! Don't move!
- Anyone?!

16
00:00:47,650 --> 00:00:50,530
- Taking the few who remain...
- Run!

17
00:00:51,049 --> 00:00:52,723
- on a journey...
- What the hell is going on?

18
00:00:52,753 --> 00:00:54,022
through time.

19
00:00:54,052 --> 00:00:57,152
We're either in the past
or we're in the future.

20
00:01:01,416 --> 00:01:02,640
Now...

21
00:01:03,562 --> 00:01:05,821
- flash forward.
- We made a mistake.

22
00:01:05,941 --> 00:01:07,850
- Three years have passed.
- Somebody knows we're lying.

23
00:01:07,880 --> 00:01:09,778
The people I left behind
need our help.

24
00:01:09,808 --> 00:01:12,383
- And those who made it home...
- It wants us to come back.

25
00:01:12,413 --> 00:01:13,613
What is this place?

26
00:01:13,813 --> 00:01:17,594
- find a way back...
- Ajira Airways flight 3-1-6.

27
00:01:17,998 --> 00:01:19,186
to save their friends...

28
00:01:19,216 --> 00:01:20,908
You have a bit of a
journey ahead of you.

29
00:01:20,938 --> 00:01:24,188
- to change their fate...
- Now I know why I'm here.

30
00:01:24,426 --> 00:01:27,104
- to fulfill...
- You might wanna fasten your seat belt.

31
00:01:27,134 --> 00:01:28,703
their destiny.

32
00:01:29,929 --> 00:01:31,670
There's no turning back now.

33
00:01:31,700 --> 00:01:35,400
